{"type": "game", "name": "Bit Blaster XL", "steam_appid": 433950, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "dlc": [548700], "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/001.gif?t=1741248052\" /><i> </i>A throwback to the quarter-munching arcade hits of the '80s, <strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong> is a fast-paced, addictive shoot 'em up with a modern twist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/SteamGIFHeadersV2_gameplay.jpg?t=1741248052\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your ship <strong>never stops moving</strong>\u2014turn, boost, and brake to dodge enemies and stay alive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fire automatically</strong>\u2014focus on dodging and collecting power-ups.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gather ammo and power-ups</strong> to unleash devastating attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Earn coins</strong> to unlock new ships, each with unique speed, fire rate, and shields.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chase high scores</strong> in endless survival mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/SteamGIFHeadersV2_features.jpg?t=1741248052\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Easy to Learn, Hard to Master</strong> \u2013 Simple controls, deep gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No Twin-Stick Needed</strong> \u2013 Classic arcade-style movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Massive Power-Ups</strong> \u2013 Heat-seekers, lasers, spread shots, bombs, shields, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlockable Ships</strong> \u2013 Each with distinct playstyles and advantages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bullet Hell Intensity</strong> \u2013 Dodge waves of enemies and projectiles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Leaderboards &amp; Achievements</strong> \u2013 Compete for the top spot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong> \u2013 Earn emoticons &amp; profile wallpapers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Steam Cloud Support</strong> \u2013 Pick up where you left off.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple Languages</strong> \u2013 Available in English, Russian, German, Italian, Portuguese, French, Simplified Chinese, and Spanish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Retro Soundtrack by Spiff Tune</strong> \u2013 Unique chiptunes for each ship (free DLC).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Inspired by the Best:\u00a0</strong>Classic hits like <strong>Luftrausers, Asteroids, Space Invaders, Galaxian,</strong> and <strong>Geometry Wars</strong> influence <strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong>\u2019s addictive gameplay and retro charm.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/SteamGIFHeadersV2_devnote.jpg?t=1741248052\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong> is a simple, replayable score-chaser designed for arcade fun. If you find an issue or just want to say hi, reach out via Discord or my website\u2014I appreciate your feedback!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thanks for playing!<br><strong>Adam Nickerson - Adamvision Studios</strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/001.gif?t=1741248052\" /><i> </i>A throwback to the quarter-munching arcade hits of the '80s, <strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong> is a fast-paced, addictive shoot 'em up with a modern twist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/SteamGIFHeadersV2_gameplay.jpg?t=1741248052\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your ship <strong>never stops moving</strong>\u2014turn, boost, and brake to dodge enemies and stay alive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fire automatically</strong>\u2014focus on dodging and collecting power-ups.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gather ammo and power-ups</strong> to unleash devastating attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Earn coins</strong> to unlock new ships, each with unique speed, fire rate, and shields.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chase high scores</strong> in endless survival mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/SteamGIFHeadersV2_features.jpg?t=1741248052\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Easy to Learn, Hard to Master</strong> \u2013 Simple controls, deep gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No Twin-Stick Needed</strong> \u2013 Classic arcade-style movement.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Massive Power-Ups</strong> \u2013 Heat-seekers, lasers, spread shots, bombs, shields, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unlockable Ships</strong> \u2013 Each with distinct playstyles and advantages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bullet Hell Intensity</strong> \u2013 Dodge waves of enemies and projectiles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Leaderboards &amp; Achievements</strong> \u2013 Compete for the top spot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Steam Trading Cards</strong> \u2013 Earn emoticons &amp; profile wallpapers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Steam Cloud Support</strong> \u2013 Pick up where you left off.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple Languages</strong> \u2013 Available in English, Russian, German, Italian, Portuguese, French, Simplified Chinese, and Spanish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Retro Soundtrack by Spiff Tune</strong> \u2013 Unique chiptunes for each ship (free DLC).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Inspired by the Best:\u00a0</strong>Classic hits like <strong>Luftrausers, Asteroids, Space Invaders, Galaxian,</strong> and <strong>Geometry Wars</strong> influence <strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong>\u2019s addictive gameplay and retro charm.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/extras/SteamGIFHeadersV2_devnote.jpg?t=1741248052\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bit Blaster XL</strong> is a simple, replayable score-chaser designed for arcade fun. If you find an issue or just want to say hi, reach out via Discord or my website\u2014I appreciate your feedback!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thanks for playing!<br><strong>Adam Nickerson - Adamvision Studios</strong></p>", "short_description": "Bit Blaster XL is a fast-paced, retro arcade shoot 'em up (shmup) inspired by the classic quarter-munchers of the \u201880s. Easy to pick up, hard to put down\u2014boost, dodge, shoot, and chase high scores in this addictive, old-school action game!", "supported_languages": "English, French, Italian, German, Spanish - Spain, Portuguese - Portugal, Russian, Simplified Chinese, Portuguese - Brazil", "reviews": "\u201cTo put it simply, Bit Blaster XL is an addictive experience.\u201d<br>OP Noobs<br><br>\u201cGreat addition to the Steam library. For .99 it doesn't get much better than this.\u201d<br>Game Review Journal<br><br>\u201c...delivers an enjoyable arcade experience without the frustration.\u201d<br>The Australian Times<br>", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/78163a0d17719e45ec372fffe960478bc84183cf/header.jpg?t=1741248052", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/63d3c64e835629f99ae77e4a521826888088217e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1741248052", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/433950/63d3c64e835629f99ae77e4a521826888088217e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1741248052", "website": "http://www.adamvisionstudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows 7<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Dual Core +<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 512MB +<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 500 MB available space<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> Is your computer older than ten years? You should probably get a new computer before you consider more games.</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10 (why not recommend the newest?)<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Got four cores? Great! Bit Blaster XL will run smooth on most things, but especially on four cores.<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> Something within the last five years would be nice and gorgeous, better is always better.<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 501 MB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> I made a bunch of these bit blaster xl sound effects by making stupid noises with my mouth into a pretty low rent consumer microphone, so I recommend not having a sound card, or you may realize this.<br></li><li><strong>Additional Notes:</strong> When you do things right, people won't be sure you've done anything at all.</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<